column2: SELECT u.SN_name, u.ra, u.dec,     p.elpetro_kcorrect_f, p.elpetro_kcorrect_n, elpetro_kcorrect_u,     p.elpetro_kcorrect_g, elpetro_kcorrect_r, elpetro_kcorrect_i,     p.elpetro_kcorrect_z FROM mydb.Host_Gals_SNf as u  LEFT JOIN nsatlas as p on (ABS(p.ra-u.ra)<# AND ABS(p.dec-u.dec)<#)  ORDER BY u.SN_name asc  INTO mydb.Host_Gals_SNf_kcorr
